lank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/07140817\/Cathedral-evora-portugal.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"h-3-the-university-of-evora\">3. The University of Evora<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This is a really unique place to visit in Evora, especially as it is the second oldest university in Portugal. Wander among the amazing archways and courtyards, and admire the colorful Azulejos tiles that decorate the classrooms. An absolute must-see is the university library; its ceiling looks like a work of art!<\/p>\n\n\n\n\n<a class=\"block-googlemaps\" title=\"Get our Google Maps Legend\" data-maptype=\"Portugal \" href=\"\/shop\/google-maps\/portugal\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n            <div class=\"block-googlemaps__container\">\n                <div class=\"block-googlemaps__content\">\n                    <span class=\"block-googlemaps__title\">Our Portugal  tips in your Google Maps?<\/span>\n                    <span class=\"block-googlemaps__text\">We made it easier for you! All our tips: favourite to do's, restaurants, hikes, secret spots &amp; more in Google Maps!<\/span>\n                    <span class=\"block-googlemaps__button\">Shop our Maps <svg class=\"icon\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg><\/span>\n                    <span class=\"block-googlemaps__notice\" style=\"display:none; font-size:12px; margin-top:15px;\">The map for this destination will be available soon. Thank you for your interest!<\/span>\n                <\/div>\n                <img class=\"block-googlemaps__image lazyload\" tempsrc=\"\/build\/images\/google-maps-banner-image.png\" alt=\"google maps phone\">\n            <\/div>\n        <\/a><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p><strong>Tip<\/strong>: The university is open to the public, despite students continuing to study here. Because of this, be respectful of students who are working. Better still, choose lunchtime to visit as the rooms will be quieter.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--attractions \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--attractions\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Entrance Fee:<\/strong> 3 EUR<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n            <a href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\/pin\/create\/button\/?url=https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/53683&amp;media=https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/07200527\/evora-portugal-travel-guide-1.jpg\" class=\"block-pinterest\" title=\"Save this article on Pinterest\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n                <div class=\"block-pinterest__container\">\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__content\">\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__title\">No time to read now? <\/div>\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__subtitle\">No worries! Save on Pinterest to read it later.<\/div>\n                        <span class=\"block-pinterest__button\">Save<span class=\"visible-desktop\">&#xA0;to Pinterest<\/span> <svg class=\"icon\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg><\/span>\n                    <\/div>\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__image-wrap\"><img src=\"\/build\/images\/blank.png\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/07200527\/evora-portugal-travel-guide-1-17x30.jpg\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/07200527\/evora-portugal-travel-guide-1-338x600.jpg\" class=\"lazyload block-pinterest__image\" alt=\"Evora, Portugal: A Travel Guide to the Historical Treasure\" height=\"600\" width=\"338\">\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/a>\n\n\n<h2 id=\"h-4-wander-the-pretty-streets\">4. Wander the Pretty Streets<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Evora is so beautiful that it would be easy to spend several days here wandering its streets and soaking up the atmosphere. The slow pace of life, and the endless sunshine and flowers, make it feel like summer every day.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--hotels \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--hotels\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/evora-hotels-all\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">See all the hotels to stay in Evora<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/07130434\/evora-portugal-streets-europe.jpg\" alt=\"evora portugal streets europe\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"evora portugal streets europe\" class=\"wp-image-55274 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/07130434\/evora-portugal-streets-europe.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/07130434\/evora-portugal-streets-europe-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/07130434\