aps\/EgzkAqhwtfiqwhqJA\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Praca do Giraldo<\/a>), where you&#x2019;ll find the fountain. It has 8 spouts that represent each of the streets that lead away from the square. Wander up one of the streets and discover white houses with yellow painted trim, terracotta roofs, pink flowers, and Azulejo tiles. <\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Read: <\/strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/portugal\/obidos-portugal\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Obidos &#x2013; one of Portugal&#x2019;s most beautiful villages!<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/07130502\/evora-streets-540x810.jpg\" alt=\"evora streets\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"evora streets\" class=\"wp-image-55278 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 540px) 100vw, 540px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/07130502\/evora-streets-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/07130502\/evora-streets-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/07130502\/evora-streets-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/07130502\/evora-streets-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourha