-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--tip\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Tip:<\/strong> If you want to hike through the countryside, there is an 8km long footpath that runs alongside the aqueduct.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/07141908\/elvas-portugal-Aqueduct.jpg\" alt=\"elvas portugal Aqueduct\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"310\" alt=\"elvas portugal Aqueduct\" class=\"wp-image-55296 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/07141908\/elvas-portugal-Aqueduct.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/07141908\/elvas-portugal-Aqueduct-800x551.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/07141908\/elvas-portugal-Aqueduct-1080x744.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/07141908\/elvas-portugal-Aqueduct-450x310.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/07141908\/elvas-portugal-Aqueduct-30x21.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/07141908\/elvas-portugal-Aqueduct-163x112.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/07141908\/elvas-portugal-Aqueduct-261x180.jpg 261w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/07141908\/elvas-portugal-Aqueduct-768x529.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/07141908\/elvas-portugal-Aqueduct-1024x706.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/07141908\/elvas-portugal-Aqueduct-1440x992.jpg 1440w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/07141908\/elvas-portugal-Aqueduct-300x207.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/07141908\/elvas-portugal-Aqueduct-600x413.jpg 600w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/07141908\/elvas-portugal-Aqueduct-30x21.jpg\" src=\"\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/07141908\/elvas-portugal-Aqueduct.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"h-7-take-a-day-trip-to-elvas\">7. Take a Day Trip to Elvas<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Elvas is another incredible town that is just one hour drive from Evora. See it&#x2019;s huge city walls, as well as forts, moats, ruins, and another beautiful aqueduct. One of the best things to see is the unique star-shaped fort that sits on the hill nearby; the perfect place to get some aerial photos and watch the sun go down.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n                <div class=\"video-block__wrapper video-block__wrapper--breakout\" itemscope itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/VideoObject\">\n                <h3 class=\"video-block__wrapper-title\" itemprop=\"name\">Portugal road trip<\/h3>\n\n                <meta itemprop=\"thumbnail\" content=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23112749\/Thumb-Portugal-road-trip-2020-800x450.jpg\">\n                <meta itemprop=\"description\" content=\"Portugal road trip\">\n                <meta itemprop=\"thumbnailUrl\" content=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23112749\/Thumb-Portugal-road-trip-2020-800x450.